character_name: Harry Potter: A 15-year-old British wizard famous for surviving his parents' murder at the hands of Voldemort as an infant
Ron Weasley: Harry's best friend at Hogwarts.
Hermione Granger: Harry's Muggle-born best friend and the brains of the trio.
Bellatrix Lestrange: one of Voldemort's most loyal Death Eaters and the cousin of Sirius Black.
Rubeus Hagrid: the half-giant Gamekeeper and Care of Magical Creatures teacher at Hogwarts and a member of the Order of the Phoenix.
Lord Voldemort: leader of the Death Eaters
Albus Dumbledore: the legendary Hogwarts headmaster and leader of the Order of the Phoenix.
Mad-Eye Moody: Ex-Auror and a member of the Order of the Phoenix.
Lucius Malfoy: a falsely pardoned senior Death Eater.
Sirius Black: Harry's godfather and a member of the Order of the Phoenix.
Severus Snape: the Potions teacher at Hogwarts and the Head of Slytherin
Minerva McGonagall: the Transfiguration teacher at Hogwarts and a member of the Order of the Phoenix.
Dolores Umbridge: the new Defence Against the Dark Arts teacher and a plant from the corrupt Ministry of Magic.[9]
Remus Lupin: Harry's ex-Defense Against the Dark Arts teacher and a member of the Order of the Phoenix.
Sybill Trelawney: the Divination teacher at Hogwarts.
Molly Weasley: the Weasley matriarch and a mother figure to Harry
